data.description: NEW PRICE, hurry! Corner lot Traditional Home that Exemplifies Character and Curb Appeal with Victorian Accents! Open feeling layout on the main with vaulted family room and cozy wood burning fireplace. Newer LVP flooring on main. Newer carpeting upstairs. Newer A/C and Furnace in 2017. Smart home security system on outside. Walking paths/sidewalks lead to all 3 schools.
